# auto generated gallery with lightbox
ref: https://jekyllcodex.org/without-plugin/image-gallery/  
ref: https://jekyllcodex.org/without-plugin/lightbox/# 


# add new gallery page
1 add event.html under /assets/gallery/event.html  
2 add items under /assets/gallery/gallery.html  
3 put images in sub image folder under images


